column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name],     &&& + cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec,    dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,    p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z  FROM #upload u       JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id       JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID        JOIN sppparams sp ON p.fluxobjid = sp.specobjid ORDER BY x.up_id SELECT top # so.bestobjid, so.specobjid, so.plate, so.mjd, so.fiberid,  sp.teffadop, sp.fehadop, sp.loggadop, sp.snr, sp.flag   FROM specobjall so  JOIN sppparams sp ON so.specobjid = sp.specobjid and so.sciencePrimary=#  WHERE sp.teffadop > # and sp.teffadop < #  and fehadop > # and fehadop < #  and loggadop > # and loggadop < #  and sp.flag like &&&  and sp.snr > #
